The fitting results are presented in Fig. S8 and Table S3. Obviously, b-values of all the electrode materials are close to 0.5, indicating the diffusion-controlled behavior and battery-type charge–discharge process. It is worth mentioning that Eq. 3 is originated from Eq. 4 [21]:4i=iEDLC+idiff=k1v+k2v0.5\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
